    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Investigate a CIA Scenario\r\n\r\nUse this AI Chat level to help you with your case files investigations, as the attacker, defender, or together.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Tell AI chat: \r\n\t- Which case file you are working on\r\n    - The role you are playing (attacker or defender)\r\n    - Your question\r\n\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need help understanding what you can ask AI Chat for help with?**]\r\nYou can ask AI chat if:\r\n - You’re stuck on why the failure matters\r\n - You need help deciding on solutions or tradeoffs\r\n - You want AI Chat to help you recognizing patterns. (For this one you may want to upload your completed activity guide table.)\r\n:::\r\n",
    "submittable": "false",
